        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on QdeB’s <hi rend="italic">Unité de l’espèce humaine</hi> [1861].</p> 
            <p>Discusses acceptance of his theory among scientists, especially geologists.</p>
            <p>C. V. Naudin did not show how selection applied in nature, but Patrick Matthew clearly anticipated CD’s views.</p>
        </abstract>
